*Deni* je istina da su moji roditelji izmislili priču. (It is true that my parents invented a story.)

*Denija* je bila lepa, ali i strašna. (The story was beautiful, but also scary.)

*Deniju* nikada nećemo zaboraviti. (We will never forget the story.)

*Denijem* su nas naučili važne lekcije. (The story taught us important lessons.)

*Denijama* smo se i smejali i plakali. (We both laughed and cried with the stories.)